data.description: Want to get out of town? Stunning panoramic Cascade Mountain views like this are hard to find! This private 15+ acre stick built home is located about 45 minutes east of Prineville and 20 minutes from Prineville Reservoir. Built in 1999, it has a very open concept with plenty of window lighting facing the Cascades and new flooring throughout. New paint in 2022. Large primary with slider to the side yard.. Attached garage, storage shed. Take a minute on the back patio and watch the sunset. If you're looking for privacy with the views, come take a look!
